{"tid":813198,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴車長撞斃女途人囚20個月  裝修工人高院菜刀威嚇法官囚16個月","createTime":"2018-09-10T09:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T14:20:42.000Z","uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bb968bcc5b725553285df58bae7a6364e4136f4b","tid":813198,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180910/58664540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F58664540&d=QdAYs1uv84AQAC4BClgFMEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=cadf02e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F58664540&h=dc2c9f0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180910/58664540</a><br />\n<br />\n九巴車長清晨6時由尖沙咀總站駕駛1A線頭班車，開車未幾便兩度嘔吐，結果離開站頭三分鐘即鏟上行人路撞斃女途人，案件經審訊後，法官早前指車長明知嚴重不適仍繼續駕駛，罔顧其他道路使用者安危，裁定他危險駕駛導致他人死亡罪成。法官今判刑指案件嚴重，惟與藥駕、酒駕或刻意超速等案件不同，被告案發後患上創傷後遺症要看精神及心理醫生，決定判20個月監禁及停牌5年。<br />\n<br />\n被告梁衞剛（42歲）以往有6項案底，包括盜竊和藏毒，最後一次是2002年因藏毒被判監27個月；交通案底則是2015年的駕駛時使用手提電話。辯方早前求情稱，被告在2007年開始任職巴士司機，交通紀錄良好，對上一次案底已是10多年前，顯然他已重新做人，望能輕判。法官今透露，巴士公司曾多次對被告發出警告，但因屬巴士公司內部事宜，法庭判刑時不作考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5b962c23e60383cc04e93fb6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5b962c23e60383cc04e93fb6&d=QdAYs1uv84AQAC4BClgFMEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=99c99155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5b962c23e60383cc04e93fb6</a><br />\n<br />\n一名裝修工人去年十月在高等法院以菜刀威嚇法官，被裁定刑事毀壞罪名成立，判囚16個月。  案件在區域法院審理，53歲被告余祖林涉嫌去年10月17日，在高等法院以菜刀威嚇法官陳嘉信，又用刀劈向法官席前的桌子。他同日由立法會議員林卓廷陪同，到灣仔警署自首。  區域法院裁定被告刑事毀壞罪名成立，其餘兩項刑事恐嚇及管有攻擊性武器罪名不成立。法官稱量刑為18個月，考慮到被告承認部分控罪，扣減刑期至16個月。"},{"pid":"74d433dc4fbdb35e41e72299f7a844fcfd523897","tid":813198,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211bbf1744c185b342f59ae249033133edcb4d7c","tid":813198,"uid":54884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"嚇法官要判重d"},{"pid":"15d4015fc58e0f963d3f13f9d8555c4f8f3f8204","tid":813198,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:23:19.000Z","msg":"蠢左啦 揸車撞死個官化算啲"},{"pid":"bc0f3cc629416c4d2200fb4d1cd1a6dcc5a9db9a","tid":813198,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"15d4015fc58e0f963d3f13f9d8555c4f8f3f8204","tid":813198,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:23:19.000Z","msg":"蠢左啦 揸車撞死個官化算啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"咁又唔同判法了，咪傻啦"},{"pid":"ea0b8fb8e13c3d80982b07468c137886e95d9a9d","tid":813198,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15d4015fc58e0f963d3f13f9d8555c4f8f3f8204","tid":813198,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:23:19.000Z","msg":"蠢左啦 揸車撞死個官化算啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aacb922d8d9971449f9fee900d7d1ddefa06a3a","tid":813198,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T10:00:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6641870afcf16d1f223498208a23ad42ba104943","tid":813198,"uid":3167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T10:02:05.000Z","msg":"做官死全家"},{"pid":"89ae177e0b1b5ccd5d86a3e794ba26519c62cce7","tid":813198,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"旺角大襲警：7年"},{"pid":"ecf8dbda9519966159e89d695d084a2b54b22d0a","tid":813198,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea0b8fb8e13c3d80